{"tid":909631,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Groupmate突然消失，今日撞到佢","createTime":"2018-11-20T13:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T04:49:18.000Z","uid":82344,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"17fad0ea6e57797fc0a0dd7d98b5112a1f862bd2","tid":909631,"uid":82344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:56:02.000Z","msg":"功課唔交，上堂唔出現，wts潛水，突然消失咗幾日<br />\n今日喺學校附近見返，成個人極之頹喪<br />\n我叫佢，佢調頭走，我身為gpmate一個就費事追，同埋我覺得佢想靜就應該比人靜下，不過係咪應該追？<br />\n嚟緊有個present,但係少問題，冇左佢唔會成唔到事<br />\n只係呢個情況我想講出嚟，問下大家應該點做？"},{"pid":"9b1005455e4c713d36376ec939f40a7a8dfa260e","tid":909631,"uid":30836,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:58:00.000Z","msg":"拆夥囉<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">😥</span>"},{"pid":"d18e9dcffe50c60dc36481486a941972029a6628","tid":909631,"uid":218609,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:58:50.000Z","msg":"告鳩佢唔做野啦，仲要問？<br />\n你同佢有親？"},{"pid":"68bca0033100c6271cdcd73a2c8eed56bfca4da6","tid":909631,"uid":37299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n曾經係個個見到同學調頭跑走既人"},{"pid":"b094a691daf973f639c3310dd962f93451deead7","tid":909631,"uid":182397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T14:00:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32dee4386c2fd0970ae9ac1ff58e63051c1bf785","tid":909631,"uid":42986,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T14:01:54.000Z","msg":"同tutor講 佢可能有情緒病 呢個時候應該係學校要介入提供support"},{"pid":"be9649f3c957339ee8be478c45fb3bc45b7b6614","tid":909631,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T14:03:14.000Z","msg":"我都試過 最後佢quit埋"},{"pid":"32e741fbd4f0af6abbcb1048ba6b25dc8d71619c","tid":909631,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T14:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋我覺得佢想靜就應該比人靜下，不過係咪應該追？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁佢係想freeride係咪就俾佢freeride？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gi